value:
Royal...family? You're REAL nobles?!
Hey, Virion, I need you! I need some
dignified greetings to use!

I mentioned my goal was Hollywood
and they asked me if that's the name
of some kind of exotic food!$k$pIs this...culture shock?

Thanks for all the patrolling you do!
If you're tired, try a smoothie. That's
what they do in Hollywood, y'know!

I can remember every line I've ever
performed with perfect accuracy.
I'll recite them all now, if you'd like.

Shopping, festivals... There's just so
much fun to be had here! But i-it's
not like I'm just having fun though!$k$pFamiliarity with everyday activities
is essential for us actors, you see.

Here's how showbiz types greet each
other... "Hey, can I tell you about my
screenplay?" Huh? ...You don't get it?$k$pWell...$Nf says hi.
Just as expected! For me, anyway.

I can't stop now. I haven't reached
my dreams yet!
Completely unacceptable! Just...ugh!

A perfect fit for my limitless talent!
...Thank you for all your support,
of course.

I'm Eleonora Yumizuru, a star in the
making. Having me on your side
assures wins worthy of Hollywood!

Ah! On patrol again, I see. Me? I was
just thinking about something...$k$pThis world is like a movie! There's a
collection of unique, chosen heroes,
all working toward the same thing...$k$pI was just trying to figure out who
would make the best supporting
cast... I'd be the star, of course.$k$pThat's me! The beautiful girl destined
to be lost in another world...$k$pBut there's one important role that
I haven't cast yet... The leader of the
gathered heroes! Hm... Who to cast?$k$pHuh? ...You don't know either? Wow.
For such a "brilliant" summoner, you
sure can be dim!
Take this!
Hit!
きゃ！
Just a scratch!
I only need one shot!
Away with you!
This one's all mine, Virion!
$nMPID_ヴィオール|A most refined maneuver!
$nMPID_ヴィオール|Strike with grace and precision!
$nMPID_ヴィオール|Let us end this, my dear!
I can't...die here...
Hmmm?
Call me Elly, OK? That's what they'll call me in Hollywood.
No more horror movies for me. I can't take it!
Acting is challenging, but the best way to do it is to disappear completely into your role.
I can't take my eyes off you. My heart races whenever I... *laugh* Sorry, just practicing.
Virion is great most of the time, but the way he goes on about nobility does get on my nerves.
This is your debut into high society. Seize the moment, my dear Elly!
Is there no one who can show my dear Elly the bearing of a proper lady?
With hands like these, no other Virion is nobler than I!
I hope Fortuna's doing OK back home.
I can't thank you enough for staying by my side.
Count me in!
Is that my cue?
At once.
Allow me.
